ground.schema:
Node properties:
Question {link: STRING, accepted_answer_id: INTEGER, creation_date: INTEGER, view_count: INTEGER, answer_count: INTEGER, body_markdown: STRING, uuid: INTEGER, title: STRING}
User {uuid: INTEGER, display_name: STRING}
Tag {name: STRING, link: STRING}
Answer {link: STRING, title: STRING, is_accepted: BOOLEAN, body_markdown: STRING, score: INTEGER, uuid: INTEGER}
Comment {score: INTEGER, uuid: INTEGER, link: STRING}
Relationship properties:

The relationships:
(:Question)-[:TAGGED]->(:Tag)
(:User)-[:ASKED]->(:Question)
(:User)-[:COMMENTED]->(:Comment)
(:User)-[:PROVIDED]->(:Answer)
(:Answer)-[:ANSWERED]->(:Question)
(:Comment)-[:COMMENTED_ON]->(:Question)
